------

“感知-认知-执行”的端到端闭环解决方案，在制造生成、灾难响应太空中获取



Mithril is a next-generation space infrastructure company. We focus on designing, building, and operating highly resilient satellite constellations and key components that form the reliable backbone for global connectivity, Earth observation, and in-orbit services.

秘银公司是一家新一代太空基础设施企业。我们专注于设计、建造和运营高韧性的卫星星座与关键部件，为全球通信、地球观测及在轨服务构建可靠的基础。

"Mithril" Standard |“秘银”标准

 "Mithril Standard" represents a commitment to unmatched orbital resilience. This encompasses radiation-hardened components, intelligent autonomous systems, and designs that ensure longevity and reliability in the harsh environment of space.

“秘银标准”代表着对无与伦比的轨道韧性的承诺。这包括抗辐射组件、智能自主系统，以及确保在严酷太空环境中长期可靠运行的设计。

Mission & Vision | 使命与愿景

• Mission: To forge the resilient foundation for humanity's future in space by deploying and maintaining ultra-reliable orbital assets that empower global progress.

  ◦ 使命： 通过部署和维护赋能全球发展的超可靠轨道资产，为人类太空未来锻造坚韧基石。

• Vision: To become the world's most trusted partner for critical space infrastructure, recognized for setting the benchmark in orbital resilience and technological elegance.

  ◦ 愿景： 成为全球关键太空基础设施最值得信赖的合作伙伴，以设定轨道韧性与技术卓越的标杆

Core Values | 核心价值

• Resilience First: Our systems are engineered to withstand, adapt, and endure.

• Ingenious Simplicity: We pursue elegant and robust solutions to complex challenges.

• Orbital Stewardship: We are committed to the long-term sustainability and security of the space domain.



Key Terminology | 关键术语

• Resilient Constellations: Our primary product offering.

• The Mithril Standard: Our benchmark for quality and durability.

• Orbital Forge: A conceptual term for our R&D and manufacturing ethos.

• Tagline

  ◦ Forging Resilience in Orbit.

  ◦ The Mithril Standard for Space.





